setInvokerOptimizationEnabled(boolean) - クラス org.mozilla.javascript.ClassCache のメソッド
推奨されていません。 The method does nothing. Invoker optimization is no longer used by Rhino. On modern JDK like 1.4 or 1.5 the disadvatages of the optimization like incresed memory usage or longer initialization time overweight small speed increase that can be gained using generated proxy class to replace reflection.
